title: Tropical Sunset Cocktail
ingredients: ['8 cubes ice', '2 tablespoons dark rum', '2 tablespoons white rum', '2 tablespoons coconut flavoured rum', '2 dashes grenadine syrup', '2 tablespoons orange juice', '2 tablespoons pineapple juice', '1 dash lemon juice', '1 dash dry vermouth', '1 cocktail cherry', '1 lemon slice', '1 orange slice']
